data.description:
*Call Ryan Chyzy 405.627.1676 for more information* 
Wow! Must checkout this amazing floor plan with time to customize! Built by one of the best builders in the state with great attention to detail, this home will feature all the bells and whistles someone could ever need in their new home. Enter the home and you will be greeted with an open floor plan with wood-look tile throughout. Living room will have high ceilings with custom feature and stone fireplace. Kitchen will feature custom cabinetry, large island, high end stainless steel appliances, pantry and spacious eat-in kitchen area. Master suite will include an upscale bathroom with double vanities, soaking tub, walk-in shower and walk-in closet. Large bonus room upstairs with bathroom. Oversized covered back patio, tankless water heater and underground sprinkler come standard in each home. A few of many energy efficient features include blown-in insulation, 95% EE HVAC system, Low E windows, solar decking and more. Contact soon to see floor plan in person and pick your colors!
